fields.name: AgentName
fields.description: Name of the Agent assigned to this run.

fields.name: AgentResourceId
fields.description: Fully qualified resource id of the Agent assigned to this run.

fields.name: BytesExcluded
fields.description: Bytes of data that will not be transferred, as they are excluded by user configuration.

fields.name: BytesFailed
fields.description: Bytes of data that were attempted to transfer and failed.

fields.name: BytesNoTransferNeeded
fields.description: Bytes of data that will not be transferred, as they are already found on target (e.g. mirror mode).

fields.name: BytesScanned
fields.description: Bytes of data scanned so far in source.

fields.name: BytesTransferred
fields.description: Bytes of data successfully transferred to target.

fields.name: BytesUnsupported
fields.description: Bytes of data that will not be transferred, as they are unsupported on target.

fields.name: Error
fields.description: Error details.

fields.name: ExecutionEndTime
fields.description: End time of the run. Null if Agent has not reported that the job has ended.

fields.name: ExecutionStartTime
fields.description: Start time of the run. Null if no Agent reported that the job has started.

fields.name: ItemsExcluded
fields.description: Number of items that will not be transferred, as they are excluded by user configuration.

fields.name: ItemsFailed
fields.description: Number of items that were attempted to transfer and failed.

fields.name: ItemsNoTransferNeeded
fields.description: Number of items that will not be transferred, as they are already found on target (e.g. mirror mode).

fields.name: ItemsScanned
fields.description: Number of items scanned so far in source.

fields.name: ItemsTransferred
fields.description: Number of items successfully transferred to target.

fields.name: ItemsUnsupported
fields.description: Number of items that will not be transferred, as they are unsupported on target.

fields.name: JobDefinitionProperties
fields.description: Copy of parent Job Definition's properties at time of Job Run creation.

fields.name: LastStatusUpdate
fields.description: The last updated time of the Job Run.

fields.name: ProvisioningState
fields.description: The provisioning state of this resource.

fields.name: ScanStatus
fields.description: The status of Agent's scanning of source.

fields.name: SourceName
fields.description: Name of source Endpoint resource. This resource may no longer exist.

fields.name: SourceProperties
fields.description: Copy of source Endpoint resource's properties at time of Job Run creation.

fields.name: SourceResourceId
fields.description: Fully qualified resource id of source Endpoint. This id may no longer exist.

fields.name: Status
fields.description: The state of the job execution.

fields.name: TargetName
fields.description: Name of target Endpoint resource. This resource may no longer exist.

fields.name: TargetProperties
fields.description: Copy of Endpoint resource's properties at time of Job Run creation.

fields.name: TargetResourceId
fields.description: Fully qualified resource id of of Endpoint. This id may no longer exist.
